<h1>Here's what you'll learn about:</h1>
<ol>
<li><p><b>Our eBook:</b> <i>How To Play the Mortgage Game, And Win!</i>
Don't know where to start? The mortgage basics are covered within this eBook.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Mortgages Over The Internet:</b> <i>You Can Be Part Of the Lending Revolution</i>
There is a growing trend toward going online to find the best mortgage. This
independent study points out great information you'll want to know about <i>before</i>
you walk into your neighborhood bank to get a home loan. It also describes some of the
many ways we're different and how the loan process has changed in the past few years.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Debt Consolidation:</b> <i>A Snowstorm Couldn't Stop This One</i>
Here's how we helped one happy couple in their quest to improve their financial situation.</p></li>
<li><p><i><b>The Seven Most Important Questions To Ask Your Lender...</b></i>
Obtaining the answers to these seven questions allows you to compare mortgage brokers.
Don't use just quoted rates and fees, although our rates are quite competitive. Take a total
view of what you're getting when considering who you hire to help you with mortgage financing.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Investor Strategy:</b> <i>No Negative Cash Flow, Instant Tax Deductions!</i>
How to be creative when beginning your real estate investment career.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Early Repayment Plan:</b> <i>An Extra $153,000 For You - Or Your Lender!</i>
Understand that little changes can result in huge savings in a mortgage cost.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Guide for the Self-Employed and Non-salaried Employees:</b> <i>Obtaining A Mortgage</i>
Many small business owners don't think they can qualify for a home loan because
their tax returns contain to many deductions leaving them with a low net salary.
Find out what we can do to help.</p></li>
<li><p><b>After a Divorce:</b> <i>A Day In Court Doesn't Take Care of All Those Loose Ends</i>
Divorce doesn't end in the courtroom. People need to move on with their lives
by separating their finances, too. We can help make this task a little easier.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Using Equity to Rebuild:</b> <i>Fire Almost Causes a Financial Disaster, too</i>
When disaster strikes, tapping home equity can bridge the gap left by some
insurance policies.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Purchasing:</b> <i>Eight Deadly Mistakes to Avoid When Buying A Home</i>
An excellent primer for those contemplating purchasing a home.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Tax Deductions:</b> <i>The Scoop on Home Financing Tax Deductions</i>
Most people don't know the tax laws regarding home financing and miss
some deductions they're entitled to take.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Overcoming a Financial Nightmare:</b> <i>How I Spent My Summer Vacation</i>
Sometimes bad things happen to good people. Here's a personal statement
you won't want to miss.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Managing Your Finances:</b> <i>How to Avoid Creeping Debt</i>
When things are going good, it's easy to spend carelessly. This article
puts forth some helpful reminders.</p></li>
<li><p><b>Overcoming negative cash flow:</b> <i>Saturday Night Lending</i>
Here's another example of how we have helped borrowers regain control
over their finances by refinancing existing debt.</p></li>
</ol>
